summary: This is an email communication from an FBI Special Agent in the New York Field Office, dated September 28, 2021, regarding the addition of new serialized items to witness folders and a 3500 file. It references attached documents including a proffer and a document containing a date of birth.

persons.name: Special Agent - FBI New York Field Office
persons.context: The sender of the email, working in the Child Exploitation/Human Trafficking unit, instructing the addition of new serialized items to case files.

events.title: Case File Export
events.description: The case file was exported, after which three new items were serialized and needed to be added to witness folders.
personsInvolved: Special Agent - FBI New York Field Office

keyFacts: The communication is from an FBI Special Agent in the New York Field Office's Child Exploitation/Human Trafficking unit.
It references three new items serialized after the case file was exported on September 22, 2021.
The agent instructs the recipient to add these items to witness folders and a 3500 file, specifically excluding an item about serving a subpoena.
Attached documents include a proffer and a document containing a date of birth.
